@neilbosworth 

Hi Neil
Is this still a requirement now after we have moved the Bureau Portal Folder. I notice that the quality of the images being uploaded is very bad. e.g. there is currently 831 images in Nico Campher's folder, with barcodes, but the Autosorter cannot sort this, and doesn't even pick up that there is a barcode because of bad image quality. If we can get the UA's to improve the quality of their images, it will help a lot, as the Autosorter will then handle it
